Microsoft Power Platform Virtual Training Day:
Fundamentals

 
 

Build the skills that enable possibilities at Microsoft Power Platform Virtual Training Day: Fundamentals from Microsoft Learn. Join us for this free training event to explore the basics of building and managing innovative business solutions with Microsoft Power Platform.

You will have the opportunity to: 

  • Understand and demonstrate the business value and core components of Microsoft Power Platform.
  • Connect your data to analyze real-time business performance.
  • Act on data and insights with custom-built apps.
  • Automate workflows to improve daily processes, regardless of your technical expertise.

Join us at an upcoming event:
30 November 2023 | 10:00 AM - 2:00 PM (GMT+8) Kuala Lumpur, Singapore, Manila


Delivery Language: English
Closed Captioning Language(s): English, Indonesia, Thai, Vietnamese

 
REGISTER TODAY >
 
 

Visit the Microsoft Virtual Training Days website to learn more about other event opportunities.

1000s of best-of-breed integrations for any use case
 
 
Tailor your tools to suit the way your teams work
The Atlassian Marketplace features 1000s of apps offering additional functionality and integrations that allow you to plug into the tools your team loves, making it even easier for work to flow. Here are a few:
• eazyBI: Create advanced reports, charts and dashboards, and visualize data
 
• AWS: Allow employees to request admin‑approved services through the AWS Service Catalog
 
• Tempo Timesheets: Automatically populate timesheets through Google/Microsoft calendar integrations
*Apps shown in this email are randomly selected and we encourage you to explore our marketplace for more.
